{"tid":2335493,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Zoom、Adobe軟體支援搭載M1晶片的Mac電腦","createTime":"2020-12-22T02:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T02:47:17.000Z","uid":2638,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f98dbd056d3b18f09d75f572b2f70d67a2c01dd1","tid":2335493,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:45:21.000Z","msg":"新的桌機版Zoom開始支援Apple Silicon處理器及搭載的Mac電腦，Adobe Photoshop及Lightroom釋出M1原生執行版本，Adobe也針對影音編輯軟體Premiere Pro推出可在M1處理器原生執行的公開Beta版<br />\n<br />\n蘋果發布自有Arm-based M1晶片及搭載該晶片的三款Mac電腦才不過一個多月，支援M1幾乎成了所有桌機軟體廠商的當務之急。本周Zoom及Adobe分別宣布主要App開始支援這款晶片。<br />\n<br />\n就在歐美進入聖誕假期周之際，視訊會議軟體Zoom昨（21）日發布最新版本App，供因防疫無法相聚的使用者和其親友視訊。新增功能除了強化整合雲端聯絡人資訊、加入會議中舉手、會議排程加入僅限授權用戶加入的選項、Zoom Phone支援SMS、MMS訊息及加入提示音等功能外，最重要的是桌機版Zoom支援Apple Silicon處理器及搭載的Mac電腦。使用者可從Zoom下載中心個別下載這個版本。<br />\n<br />\n而新版Mac版Zoom相當輕巧，未令人失望。MacRumors論壇一名用戶使用它打了2.5小時視訊電話後，電池電量僅下降17%，再打了36分鐘後，只掉了7%，意謂著Zoom在M1-based Mac電腦上每小時只耗用10-13%的電量。<br />\n<br />\n此外，網路媒體8-bit發現，Adobe本周在討論區低調宣布影音編輯軟體Premiere Pro推出可在M1處理器原生執行的首個公開Beta版，邀請用戶下載試用。Beta版Premiere Pro具備了Intel CPU版相同的核心編輯功能及workflow，像是色彩、繪圖、音效、多重相機及Productions功能等。<br />\n<br />\nThe Verge報導，在此之前，Adobe另二個產品包括Photoshop及Lightroom，皆已經釋出M1原生執行版本。<br />\n$AAPL"},{"pid":"c1148f07ce9f74a4aed60ea5125da57611f29e90","tid":2335493,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8332cd9c4862124a9c6e3afa4835ad19e9241361","tid":2335493,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"等多一年換就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bab6c33d4b3d288ce6a967179535b34f21c1d7","tid":2335493,"uid":337336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"仲要用間諜軟件Zoom?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5da15f6203755b0b979fda5c125da892986d71","tid":2335493,"uid":119512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:38:10.000Z","msg":"我有隻聽歌app Audirvana 岩岩出更新都native support m1"},{"pid":"3d78d2af0316c226556b3d2287747ff6e61b936a","tid":2335493,"uid":5787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"Intel 好快收皮<br />\n然後Intel撚就會話notebook市場根本賺唔到錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15c6a1f3dec529f7362ed1a786123693bfae1f7","tid":2335493,"uid":129385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"Adobe 含啦"},{"pid":"db74bb8a8b071c91915ced9313bc64b5f973994f","tid":2335493,"uid":35752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d78d2af0316c226556b3d2287747ff6e61b936a","tid":2335493,"uid":5787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"Intel 好快收皮<br />\n然後Intel撚就會話notebook市場根本賺唔到錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T02:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你太睇小intel係企業市場影嚮力<br />\n班企業IT infra人唔好話ARM, 連AMD cpu laptop都唔肯試...."}]}